      • Select

        public static boolean Select(Component combobox,
             java.lang.String itemtext)
        Select an item in Combo Box. Typically a verification that the item was selected is attempted.

        See Detailed Reference

        Parameters:
        combobox - Component (from App Map) to Select item from.
        itemtext - -- The combo box option to select.
        Returns:
        true if successful, false otherwise.
        See Also:
        SeleniumPlus.prevResults, TestRecordData.getStatusCode(), TestRecordData.getStatusInfo()
        Example:
         boolean success = ComboBox.Select(Map.Google.Combobox1, "ItemText");

      • CaptureItemsToFile

        public static boolean CaptureItemsToFile(Component combobox,
                         java.lang.String filename,
                         java.lang.String... params)
        Capture all items in Combo Box to a file.

        See Detailed Reference

        Parameters:
        combobox - (from App Map) to get the content.
        filename - String, The filename to save the combo box's data
        params - optional
          params[0] encoding String, The file encoding.
        Returns:
        true if successful, false otherwise.
        See Also:
        SeleniumPlus.prevResults, TestRecordData.getStatusCode(), TestRecordData.getStatusInfo()
        Example:
         boolean success = ComboBox.CaptureItemsToFile(Map.Google.Combobox1,"filename");
 boolean success = ComboBox.CaptureItemsToFile(Map.Google.Combobox1,"c:\\filename.txt","UTF-8");		 
 
 
        
 File will be created into Actuals project dir or user define location.
